com.b2international.snowowl.semanticengine.simpleast.normalform

Class AttributeNameMatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.semanticengine.simpleast.normalform.AttributeNameMatch

  • public final class AttributeNameMatch
extends Object
    Simple class to hold an attribute and its containing group, if it is grouped. If the attribute is ungrouped, the group will be NO_GROUP.
